ling in all of their\nprogenitor halos, provided that the UV background exceeds J_{21} ~ few at\nredshifts as high as z ~ 20.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Jan 2014 21:00:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-03-05"}
